'Java Program' is taking/reading inputs, processing/calculation/operation and writing/display/printing
the output.

1. file operations on 'byte data' we use 
			- FileOutputStream
			- FileInputStream
			
2. file operations on 'character data' we use 
			- FileWriter
			- FileReader
			
3. file operations on 'group of character(word)/group of bytes data' we use 
			- BufferedReader
			- BufferedReader
			- BufferedInputStream
			- BufferedOutputStream
						
4. file operations on 'object data' we use 
			- ObjectOutputStream - Serialization
			- ObjectInputStream - DeSerialization
			
			